  <brief_title>An Exploratory Study of NBI-34060 Capsules and Next Day Functioning</brief_title>
  <official_title>An Exploratory Phase IIIb, Single-Blind, Outpatient Study to Assess Next-Day Functioning in Adult Primary Insomnia Patients Following the Administration of NBI-34060 Capsules During the Night</official_title>
  <sponsors>
